name: Emoji Decorated Skull
description:
Although it may resemble the emotions and thoughts of a woman, it could be a gender-free expression of the human mind conditioned in common culture across the world.

Either as a woman you experience some or all of these or as a man you identify women with such. In either case, it's a curious form of expressionism with a hint of modern abstract art poking fun at definitions of society given to humans.

Digital Painting
1498x1498 Pixels

2016
